EmpUserProvisionProcessErr.name: EmpUserProvisionProcessErr
EmpUserProvisionProcessErr.description: Represents an employee-user provisioning process error.

AccountId.description: The ID of the Person Account linked to the employee record associated with the error.

EmployeeId.description: The ID of the employee record associated with the error.

ErrorCode.description: The error code if the provisioning isnâ€™t successful.

ErrorMessage.description: If an error occurred, this field contains the error message.

LastReferencedDate.description: The date and time when the error was last referenced, with a precision of one second.
